'''''The Coral Kingdom''''', by [[Douglas Niles]], is the second book in the [[Druidhome trilogy]].

{{quote|''An epic sea voyage... a daring rescue...''

''The [[Earthmother]] has returned to the [[Moonshae Isles|Moonshaes]].  Now her mightiest [[druid]], [[Robyn Kendrick]], faces the greatest challenge of her life.  Aided by a courageous [[Northlander|Northman]] prince, her own daughters, and a crew of heroes, Robyn wages a desperate battle against the savage [[Claws of the Deep]].''}}
